  <recipient-country code="BD" percentage="71">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Leading the implementation of core activities together with other consortium partners. There are different life story collection and collective analysis; action research and children led research groups to lead research on issues which relate to WFCL. In Bangladesh, there is a social protection pilot and participatory &apos;social protection plus&apos; activiteis in Bangladesh.</narrative>
